### Technical Architecture

**Database Schema (Prisma):**
```prisma
model User {
  id           String         @id @default(cuid())
  username     String         @unique
  password     String
  score        Int            @default(0)  // Points balance
  createdAt    DateTime       @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime       @updatedAt
